&Q000576 = Letter from Ur-Enlila to a governor and temple administrator
@composite
#project: epsd2/literary
#atf: use unicode
#atf: use math
#etcsl: text-id=c.3.3.04
#key: after http://etcsl.orinst.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/etcsl.cgi?text=c.3.3.04&display=Crit&charenc=gcirc#

1. ensi₂ saŋŋa-ra u₃-na-a-dug₄
#lem: ensik[ruler]; saŋŋa[an official]; dug[speak]
#etcsl: line-id=1

2. {m}ur-{d}en-lil₂-la₂-ke₄ na-ab-be₂-a
#lem: Urenlila[1]PN; e[speak]
#etcsl: line-id=2

3. pa₅ (1:a-luh-ha:1) a i-ib₂-tum₃
#lem: par[(small) canal]; luh[clean]; a[water]; tum[bring]
#etcsl: line-id=3

:3v.1.1: (#note: 1 ms. has instead:#) i₃-luh-ha
#lem: luh[clean]

4. (1:{m}{d}en-lil₂-diŋir-ŋu₁₀:1) u₃ ha-an-za-mu
#lem: Enlildiŋirŋu[1]PN; u[and]; Hanzamu[1]PN
#etcsl: line-id=4

:4v.1.1: (#note: 1 ms. has instead:#) {m}{d}en-lil₂-a₂-ŋu₁₀
#lem: Enlilaŋu[1]PN
:4v.1.2: (#note: another ms. has instead:#) {[m]}{[d]}en#-lil₂-la₂-ŋu₁₀
#lem: Enlilaŋu[1]PN

5. (1:ib₂-sig₃-ge-eš:1) mu-da-an-kar-re-eš
#lem: sig[put into]; kar[flee]
#etcsl: line-id=5

:5v.1.1: (#note: 1 ms. has instead:#) ib₂-sig₉-ge-eš
#lem: sig[put into]

6. {m}lugal-an-ne₂ na-ab-be₂-a
#lem: Lugalane[1]PN; e[speak]
#etcsl: line-id=6

7. ŋe₂₆-e pa₅ 1(DIŠ)-am₃ za-e pa₅ 1(DIŠ)-am₃ ensi₂ pa₅ 1(DIŠ)-am₃
#lem: ŋaʾe[I]; par[(small) canal]; n; zaʾe[you]; par[(small) canal]; n; ensik[ruler]; par[(small) canal]; n
#etcsl: line-id=7

8. a (1:he₂-mu-e-de₆:1) bi₂-dug₄ nu-mu-un-še-ge-eš
#lem: a[water]; de[carry]; dug[speak]; šeg[agree]
#etcsl: line-id=8

:8v.1.1: (#note: 1 ms. has instead:#) he₂-mu-e-dug₄
#lem: dug[speak]

9. erin₂ id₂-zu nu-ma pa₅-bi a i-ib₂-tum₃
#lem: erin[people]; id[river]; nu[not]; par[(small) canal]; a[water]; tum[bring]
#etcsl: line-id=9

10. ŋa₂-a sah₆-bi a ma-ab-tum₃
#lem: ŋaʾe[I]; zah[disappear]; a[water]; tum[bring]
#etcsl: line-id=10

11. a₂ ma-tur ia₂ ŋuruš (1:10:1) hu-mu-e-ši-in-gi₄-gi₄-ma
#lem: a[arm]; tur[small]; ya[five]; ŋuruš[young adult male]; n; gi[turn]
#etcsl: line-id=11

:11v.1.1: (#note: 1 ms. has instead:#) ŋeš₂
#lem: ŋeš[sixty]

12. a-ma-ru-kam
#lem: amaru[flood]
#etcsl: line-id=12






